rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0001
rows.name:
So Acedia's kinda disappeared, huh?
All the people who came over are
all spaced out and stuff...

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I kinda understand, though. I mean,
they lost their homes, right?

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0003
rows.name:
And like, their faith got betrayed.
People are saying that's even worse.

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0004
rows.name:
But I'm trying to cheer up the kids
who took shelter here. We're all
going swimming together and stuff!

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0005
rows.name:
We can all make friends from
swimming and then no one'll
have to be sad any more!
